    "modid": "sanitycraft",
    "modName": "SanityCraft",
    "version": "0.1.0",
    "description": "SanityCraft adds a psychological survival system to Minecraft.  Players have a sanity level that decreases in darkness, caves, storms and near hostile mobs.  Low sanity causes hallucinations, strange sounds and paranormal events.  Survive the world… or your own mind.",
    "author": "Nekuzaky",
